\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $x>0$
\end_inset

 measures the visibility/salience of actions.
 Defining 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{a}=x\gamma_{a}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{y}=x\gamma_{y}$
\end_inset

, agents solve
\begin_inset Formula 
